Requires:         R-CRAN-RColorBrewer 
Requires:         R-stats 
Requires:         R-graphics 
Requires:         R-grDevices 
Requires:         R-utils 

%description
Fits a multivariate model of decision trees for multiple, continuous
outcome variables. A model for each outcome variable is fit separately,
selecting predictors that explain covariance in the outcomes.  Built on
top of 'gbm', which fits an ensemble of decision trees to univariate
outcomes.

